text: Zsolt Dani (born 4 August 1969) is a Hungarian rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Hungary Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Szeged
